{
  "stem": "19218.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 457.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You tell him you're not home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And of course, she had no choice but to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My luck was that my mother-in-law, my future mother-in-law, which I didn't know at the time, she liked me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, she saw a Jewish guy, especially after talking, that I could read.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I could daven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "This I said for his-- [LAUGHS] for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so, anyway, we-- we dated for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we got engaged on January 18, 1952.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You-- you see, the-- the-- the-- the date 18 always was significant with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So, we got engaged that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we started planning a wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I had a problem with-- I wanted my brother to come to the wedding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But if you recall at the beginning, what my brother's-- on his mind was always the-- the last words my father said is, keep Ben always with you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And here, my brother's in Costa Rica.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I'm in the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started working on papers to get him into the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because we were working on the papers as a permanent-- as a permanent resident in the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was his brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wasn't an American citizen yet either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But because of that, he couldn't come here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were working on his papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he couldn't come as a visitor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, at the time, we-- I wrote to Senator Moody as a-- as a-- he was a senator at the time, and telling him my story.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is the only living relative I have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I realized that the papers are about to come due for him to come as a permanent resident.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my wedding is scheduled for the 26th of October, 1952.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
